Lingua-IT-Numbers version 0.06
==============================

Lingua::IT::Numbers converts arbitrary numbers into human-oriented
Italian text. It is then the Italian version of the Lingua::*::Numbers modules
that can be found on cpan.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 Regexp::Common::numbers
  
   is needed to parse number strings.

